    public class ObjectOrderMapStore<T extends io.aistac.common.canonical.data.ObjectBean>
extends ObjectMapStore<T>
    The ObjectOrderMapStore Class is a class used to Store other objects and provide a central management class for storing Beans. Beans stored must extend ObjectBean. In addition ObjectOrderMapStore also maintains the position of the stored objects and allows the objects to be placed at specific index within the store. the order of the store is then kept even through persistence.

    ObjectBean
